sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant FE as React Frontend
    participant MCP as MCP Backend
    participant AWS as AWS Cloud
    participant LLM as LLM Provider

    User->>FE: 1. Click Scan
    FE->>MCP: 2. tools/call: full_aws_scan
    MCP->>AWS: 3. boto3 calls (EC2/S3/IAM/SG/VPC — concurrent)
    AWS-->>MCP: 4. resource data (all services)

    Note over MCP: 5. Run 7 security rules internally<br/>(HIGH/MEDIUM/LOW findings)

    MCP->>LLM: 6. Summarise findings (prompt + findings JSON)
    LLM-->>MCP: 7. Plain English summary + recommendations
    MCP-->>FE: 8. findings list + health score + summary
    FE-->>User: 9. Render dashboard (panels update)

    Note over User,FE: --- User initiates Terraform fix ---

    User->>FE: 10. Select finding, click Terraform Fix
    FE->>MCP: 11. tools/call: generate_terraform_from_request
    MCP->>AWS: 12. Scan existing infra for context (VPC/SG/subnet IDs)
    AWS-->>MCP: 13. existing resource IDs
    MCP->>LLM: 14. Generate HCL prompt (with infra context)
    LLM-->>MCP: 15. Generated HCL code
    MCP-->>FE: 16. HCL + description
    FE-->>User: 17. Display HCL in code editor
